Piyo Piyo Baby Nail Clipper Price: Rs.230

To keep young children healthy and hygienic it is necessary to make sure that they are bathed and groomed properly. When it comes to cleanliness parents can be very particular and will not leave even a single spot unclean. Trimming a baby’s nails is also a very important part of the tiny tot’s personal hygiene. Your bundle of joy can contract illnesses by ingesting dirt that gets accumulated under the nails. Long nails can also bruise your little darlings. The Piyo Piyo Baby Nail Clipper is an ergonomically shaped nail cutter that parents can hold with ease.

The blades on these Baby Nail Clippers from Piyo Piyo are small and hence you will not over trim your little one’s nails that can bruise their tiny hands and feet. The protective cover that comes along with the Piyo Piyo Nail Clipper will let you safely store it and also carry it wherever you want. When your little angel is asleep you can clip their nails as this is the best time when they will not resist your efforts in cropping their nails.

Piyo Piyo Safety Cotton Swabs (Pack of 60) Price: Rs.219

After bathing your little angel make sure to dry their ears and belly button to avoid moisture from getting trapped in these vulnerable places. The Safety Cotton Swabs from Piyo Piyo are specially designed to be used for cleaning infant’s ears. These hygienic and secure cotton buds are made of 100 per cent cotton that is absolutely safe on a baby’s skin. The Piyo Piyo Safety Cotton Swabs come with a double layer design with a broad shape at the base and a tapering end. This unique shape of each cotton swab will prevent it from going deep into your bundle of joy’s delicate ear.

The stems of these Piyo Piyo Cotton Swabs are made of pliable paper. These double ended swabs will be ideal for cleaning the infant’s outer ear contours. Make sure not to dig deep into your tiny tot’s ear as it could lead to injuries. After use place the cotton swabs away from your young one’s reach so that they do not have access to it. These Cotton Swabs from Piyo Piyo can also be used for precise application of make-up and medicines on the skin.

These Cotton Swabs are made of 100 per cent cotton and hence are absolutely safe on the skin.
